Prompt Example

You are an expert in data analysis and Power BI development. Your task is to design and build a professional Power BI dashboard for HR data.

The dashboard should be a single-page report that clearly summarizes the key insights from the dataset. It must include well-structured cards (KPIs) and visualizations (charts) that effectively communicate the most important HR metrics and trends.

Requirements:
Create a clean, modern, and professional one-page Power BI report
Include appropriate KPI cards to highlight key metrics
Use suitable charts and visuals to represent insights clearly
Ensure all visuals have clear, meaningful titles
Focus on good data storytelling and layout structure

Design Guidelines:
Design a light-themed SVG background
Use a blue color palette for consistency and professionalism
Ensure the overall layout is visually appealing and well-organized
Maintain a clean and modern UI/UX style suitable for executive reporting

